{"tid":1103933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］一人一個忍笑經歷","createTime":"2019-04-12T17:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T10:32:30.000Z","uid":126511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6230ae77575aef1f566572c30bfa1037d6097352","tid":1103933,"uid":126511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"我先！<br />\n<br />\n有次同個friend炒散，因為大家都係第一次返，個阿頭就叫咗我地同另外幾個新仔埋去講下啲守則。<br />\n<br />\n因為工作環境係啲大公司幕後部門，阿頭第一句就好嚴肅咁講叫我地唔好亂睇放係枱面既文件，話有機會係商業秘密。又叫我地唔好周圍行，因為有CCTV影住，一陣見到我地出現係啲唔應該出現既地方就好麻煩。佢講得好認真，成個氣氛都好嚴肅。<br />\n<br />\n跟住唔知佢講咗句咩咩要好serious，放係枱面既siri就走咗出黎問有咩可以幫到手，一望到我已經想笑。阿頭無為意繼續講，siri就一路打佢講既野，仲要用英文輸入。我望住抽英文愈黎愈大抽，忍笑忍得好辛苦。跟住我睄到隔離個friend都忍緊笑，我終於忍唔住笑咗出聲...<br />\n<br />\n阿頭啤咗我一眼，撳熄咗siri繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，忍笑真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b6b2fd13b8e44173ec42c670a6b0021e7902e5","tid":1103933,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T18:22:31.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e344ae6489b2586053fc50323c7aa5ab8f27967","tid":1103933,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T18:23:52.000Z","msg":"好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350354e69b956575d7dbfdf4965fe56f2a902d91","tid":1103933,"uid":232594,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"同樓主差唔多<br />\n<br />\n事源有單job搞煱左，老細好嬲叫晒所有人黎訓話，爆晒粗，大聲到冧天花個隻<br />\n而負責個位同事本身個人好柒，又唔鐘意比人用粗口問候，一時火起上黎就同老細嘈，對話大概係咁：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：柒頭同事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：老細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：依家咩事先，點解你要用粗口鬧我，有錯你咪平心靜氣話我知囉？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：(好激動) 依家成壇野煱左呀，仲點平心靜氣呀，屌你老母！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：首先唔該你唔好用粗口鬧我，我唔覺得我有錯，我係做得岩既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你係撚呀？<br />\n<br />\n之後柒頭同事竟然講左一句<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔係撚！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: blue;\">屌你笑撚到我仆街 </span> (心入面)<br />\n但個氣氛實在太緊張所以唔可以笑出黎<br />\n<br />\n當時內心：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但表面：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61685c7e7d43c03fe72020e306cb211adf6205dd","tid":1103933,"uid":